About to add a read endpoint GetQuoteByRefNo in Sales/Acme.Sales.Application/Features/Quotes/. RefNo is unique (there's a DuplicateQuoteRefNoException guarding creation). Here's my draft:

```csharp
public class GetQuoteByRefNo
{
    public record Query(string RefNo) : IRequest<QuoteVm>;

    public class Handler(IAppDbContext dbContext) : IRequestHandler<Query, QuoteVm>
    {
        public async Task<QuoteVm> Handle(Query request, CancellationToken cancellationToken)
        {
            return await dbContext.Quotes
                .Where(q => q.RefNo == request.RefNo)
                .Select(q => QuoteVm.ProjectFrom(q))
                .FirstOrDefaultAsync(cancellationToken)
                ?? throw new NotFoundException(nameof(Quote), request.RefNo);
        }
    }
}
```

