Small slice: a new endpoint GetQuoteName(Guid quoteId) that returns the display name for one quote, for a tooltip. Here's my draft, which reuses the existing derivation:

```csharp
public class GetQuoteName
{
    public record Query(Guid QuoteId) : IRequest<string>;

    public class Handler(IAppDbContext dbContext) : IRequestHandler<Query, string>
    {
        public async Task<string> Handle(Query request, CancellationToken cancellationToken)
        {
            return await dbContext.Quotes
                .Where(q => q.Id == request.QuoteId)
                .Select(q => QuoteVm.ProjectFrom(q).QuoteName)
                .FirstOrDefaultAsync(cancellationToken)
                ?? throw new NotFoundException(nameof(Quote), request.QuoteId);
        }
    }
}
```

